Category:Dark Forces: Soldier for the Empire audio drama voice actors

nodes.text: Tim Russell is an actor who provided voices for the audio adaptation of the Dark Forces saga. Russell gave voice to Captain Thrawn, General Mohc and the droid A-Cee in Soldier for the Empire. Russell also voiced Captain Zyak and an unnamed bounty hunter in Rebel Agent.
